data.meta_description: The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy — Adams, Douglas, 1952-2001 — Chronicles the journeys, notions, and acquaintances of reluctant galactic traveler Arthur Dent, accompanied by never-before-published material from the late author's archives as well as commentary by famous fans.
